      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So basically, it's about who pays if there's a breach or a lawsuit. Can you give me an example of when an indemnification clause might be considered \"predatory\" or risky for a freelancer? Like, what kind of wording should I be looking out for that would be a huge red flag?",
      "source": "evaluator"
